==Покупка трамваев==
Then, place a Tramway depot, construct a vehicle by clicking ''New Vehicles'', then select a vehicle and purchase it. It will be then placed into the depot and its vehicle window will be opened. Issue [[ru/Manual/Задания]] to it, and click on the bottom bar marked "Stopped" to start the Tram. Trams can only turn around at rail end.

